WEBVTT

01:46.333 --> 01:48.834
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...
I'M SORRY.

01:48.834 --> 01:51.917
IT DOESN'T CHANGE THE FACT THAT
YOU SLEPT WITH ANOTHER WOMAN.

01:51.917 --> 01:53.333
WHAT DO THEY HAVE ON ME?

01:53.333 --> 01:55.625
THEY FOUND SOMETHING
IN YOUR CAR.

01:55.625 --> 01:57.583
OH, SHIT.

01:57.583 --> 02:00.125
Lundy: OUR PRIMARY SUSPECT
IS SOMEONE YOU KNOW WELL --

02:00.125 --> 02:01.667
SERGEANT JAMES DOAKES.

02:01.667 --> 02:03.083
HE HAD THE SLIDES.

02:03.083 --> 02:05.083
YOU KNOW ME, MARIA.
THAT'S NOT ME.

02:05.083 --> 02:06.625
DON'T YOU DISAPPEAR
ON ME, JAMES.

02:06.625 --> 02:10.166
WHAT EXACTLY IS SERGEANT DOAKES'
PROBLEM WITH YOU, MORGAN?

02:10.166 --> 02:12.750
I ALWAYS SENSED
THERE WAS SOMETHING...

02:12.750 --> 02:14.792
OFF ABOUT HIM.

02:14.792 --> 02:16.083
FROM HERE ON OUT,

02:16.083 --> 02:18.166
WE'LL WANT A PROTECTIVE DETAIL
ON YOU AT ALL TIMES.

02:18.166 --> 02:20.959
YOU'RE A GOOD COP
LIKE YOUR OLD MAN.

02:20.959 --> 02:22.583
Debra:
DO YOU THINK THEY KNOW?

02:22.583 --> 02:24.250
Lundy:
NOT UNTIL YOU TELL THEM.

02:24.250 --> 02:25.834
HE IS NOT YOUR MAN.

02:25.834 --> 02:28.041
HE MAY BE YOUR EX-PARTNER.
HE MAY BE YOUR BEST FRIEND.

02:28.041 --> 02:29.792
WHAT HE IS TO ME
IS A SUSPECT.

02:29.792 --> 02:31.125
LILA,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

02:31.125 --> 02:33.250
SHE CAME TO SEE ME, BRO.

02:33.250 --> 02:34.917
ARE YOU PISSED OR SOMETHING
ABOUT LILA AND ME?

02:34.917 --> 02:37.542
LILA'S JUST USING YOU
TO GET AT ME.
SO WHAT?

02:37.542 --> 02:40.375
Dexter: A SECRET CABIN IN
THE MIDDLE OF THE EVERGLADES --

02:40.375 --> 02:43.583
WHAT MORE COULD A REDEDICATED
SERIAL KILLER ASK FOR?

02:45.792 --> 02:48.959
JESUS CHRIST.
YOU'RE THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

02:48.959 --> 02:50.750
[ GRUNTS ]

02:50.750 --> 02:52.333
[ GUNSHOT ]

02:52.333 --> 02:54.208
AAH!

03:00.834 --> 03:03.458
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
KILL ME, MORGAN!

03:06.000 --> 03:09.291
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
FUCKING KILL ME, MORGAN!

03:17.333 --> 03:21.291
[ FROGS CROAKING,
INSECTS CHIRPING ]

03:26.667 --> 03:28.125
[ GROANS ]

03:28.125 --> 03:32.166
IS IT DEEP?
I HOPE IT'S FUCKING DEEP.

03:32.166 --> 03:36.000
IT'S A GRAZE WOUND.
MINOR TISSUE ABRASION.

03:36.000 --> 03:38.125
NO HEMORRHAGE
ALONG THE BULLET TRACK.

03:38.125 --> 03:40.250
SORRY.
I THINK I'M GONNA LIVE.

03:41.458 --> 03:42.875
AM I?

03:42.875 --> 03:44.875
THAT'S A GOOD QUESTION.

03:44.875 --> 03:47.542
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA LET ME GO,
MORGAN, THEN KILL ME NOW.

03:47.542 --> 03:48.750
JUST GET IT OVER WITH.

03:48.750 --> 03:52.875
[ Groaning ] I'D ADVISE YOU
NOT TO TEMPT ME JUST NOW.

03:52.875 --> 03:54.834
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

03:58.458 --> 04:02.041
WHY COULDN'T YOU JUST LEAVE ME
TO DO MY WORK IN PEACE?

04:02.041 --> 04:04.875
WHY'D YOU HAVE TO GO
AND RUIN EVERYTHING?

04:04.875 --> 04:07.709
YOU'RE A KILLER.
I CATCH KILLERS.

04:07.709 --> 04:10.333
SO DO I.
I CAUGHT YOU.

04:10.333 --> 04:12.250
I'M NOT A KILLER.

04:12.250 --> 04:13.583
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:13.583 --> 04:15.291
YOU ARE.

04:15.291 --> 04:18.583
THAT'S WHY YOU'VE ALWAYS KNOWN
WHAT I AM.

04:18.583 --> 04:21.375
THAT'S WHY YOU HAVE MORE
OFFICER-RELATED SHOOTINGS

04:21.375 --> 04:23.500
THAN ANYBODY ELSE.

04:23.500 --> 04:25.917
ONLY I DON'T FUCK WITH YOU
WHEN YOU SHOOT SOMEBODY.

04:25.917 --> 04:28.375
WHY COULDN'T YOU PAY ME
THE SAME PROFESSIONAL COURTESY?

04:28.375 --> 04:30.875
THERE'S NOTHING PROFESSIONAL
ABOUT WHAT YOU DO.

04:30.875 --> 04:33.166
I KILL WHEN I HAVE TO --
ON  THE JOB.

04:33.166 --> 04:35.125
OH, SO IT'S OKAY
TO TAKE A LIFE

04:35.125 --> 04:37.709
AS LONG AS YOU GET A PAYCHECK
FOR IT?

04:37.709 --> 04:39.917
THE CITY PAYS ME
TO KEEP THE LAW.

04:39.917 --> 04:42.417
I'VE GOT NEWS FOR YOU,
SERGEANT.

04:42.417 --> 04:45.959
MY CODE REQUIRES
A HIGHER STANDARD OF PROOF

04:45.959 --> 04:47.750
THAN YOUR CITY'S LAWS.

04:47.750 --> 04:49.750
AT ZERO COST
FOR THE TAXPAYER?

04:49.750 --> 04:52.750
IF YOU ASK ME,
I'M A BARGAIN.

04:52.750 --> 04:55.500
THAT'S ENOUGH BULLSHIT,
MORGAN.

04:55.500 --> 04:57.208
LET'S GET THIS OVER WITH.

04:57.208 --> 04:59.667
EITHER KILL ME
OR SET ME FREE.

04:59.667 --> 05:02.583
I ACTUALLY THINK YOU'D LIKE IT
IF I KILLED YOU,

05:02.583 --> 05:04.083
JUST TO PROVE YOUR POINT.

05:04.083 --> 05:05.333
MORGAN, YOU GOT TO CHOOSE.

05:05.333 --> 05:06.500
NO, I NEED TO GO HOME.

05:06.500 --> 05:10.333
I'VE GOT FBI GUARDS STANDING
OUTSIDE MY DOOR RIGHT NOW...

05:13.041 --> 05:15.083
...TO PROTECT ME FROM YOU.

05:16.125 --> 05:18.375
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE, MORGAN?!

05:18.375 --> 05:20.500
MORGAN, WHAT'S IT GONNA BE?!

05:20.500 --> 05:22.583
KILL ME NOW
OR SET ME FREE!

05:22.583 --> 05:24.834
YOU ONLY HAVE
TWO CHOICES, MORGAN!

05:24.834 --> 05:27.125
YOU CAN'T FUCKING IGNORE ME!

05:28.792 --> 05:30.041
WHAT'S WRONG?

05:30.041 --> 05:32.333
THE PLACE IS A GHOST TOWN
THIS EARLY.

05:32.333 --> 05:34.500
BESIDES, I THOUGHT WE WERE OUT
AS A COUPLE.

05:34.500 --> 05:38.000
OUT AND FLAUNTING IT
ARE TWO DIFFERENT THINGS.

05:38.000 --> 05:39.375
"DON'T ASK, DON'T TELL"?

05:39.375 --> 05:40.750
WORKS FOR THE MILITARY.

05:40.750 --> 05:42.625
NOT REALLY.

05:45.333 --> 05:47.625
OH, EXCELLENT.

05:47.625 --> 05:51.125
MY SUBPOENA FOR DOAKES'
PHONE RECORDS CAME THROUGH.

05:51.125 --> 05:52.834
HE ISN'T MUCH OF A TALKER.

05:52.834 --> 05:54.875
NOT A LOT OF FRIENDS,
I'M GUESSING.

05:56.375 --> 05:58.041
EXCEPT FOR ONE --
CHECK THIS OUT.

05:58.041 --> 06:00.542
THAT'S LIEUTENANT LaGUERTA'S
PHONE NUMBER,

06:00.542 --> 06:01.959
AND LOOK AT THE TIME
AND DATE.

06:01.959 --> 06:04.709
DOAKES CALLED HER RIGHT AFTER
WE LAUNCHED THE MANHUNT.

06:04.709 --> 06:06.208
WE COULD HAVE TRACED
THAT CALL.

06:06.208 --> 06:07.667
DOUBT IT.

06:07.667 --> 06:10.125
SERGEANT DOAKES WOULDN'T
HAVE STAYED ON LONG ENOUGH,

06:10.125 --> 06:12.166
BUT LaGUERTA SHOULD HAVE
GIVEN US THE CHANCE.

06:12.166 --> 06:15.291
YOU'RE GONNA REAM HER,
AREN'T YOU?

06:15.291 --> 06:16.875
CAN I BE THERE
WHEN YOU DO IT?

06:16.875 --> 06:18.166
IT'S KIND OF A HOBBY
OF MINE.

06:18.166 --> 06:20.000
YOU CAN REAM HER YOURSELF.

06:21.166 --> 06:23.166
ME?

06:23.166 --> 06:25.000
I CAN'T DRESS DOWN
MY OWN BOSS.

06:25.000 --> 06:26.875
IT'S YOUR SUBPOENA.
YOUR CASE.

06:26.875 --> 06:28.583
OUR CASE.

06:28.583 --> 06:31.417
AND I NEED TO KNOW IF YOUR
LIEUTENANT CAN BE COUNTED ON.

06:31.417 --> 06:33.041
YOU KNOW HER
BETTER THAN I DO.

06:33.041 --> 06:35.041
LOX?
UGH, GROSS.

06:35.041 --> 06:38.166
SERIOUSLY, THAT WOULD JUST
GET ME IN DEEPER SHIT WITH HER,

06:38.166 --> 06:40.208
AND LaGUERTA
ALREADY HATES ME.

06:40.208 --> 06:43.166
YOU KNOW, I'M NOT ALWAYS GONNA
BE AROUND TO RUN INTERFERENCE.

06:43.166 --> 06:44.917
OH, COME ON.

06:44.917 --> 06:47.792
YOU GOT AT LEAST FIVE,
10 GOOD YEARS LEFT IN YOU.

06:47.792 --> 06:51.583
I MEAN I WON'T BE AROUND
ONCE THIS CASE ENDS,

06:51.583 --> 06:56.041
SO A REAMING WILL BE GOOD
PRACTICE FOR YOU AFTER I'M GONE.

06:56.041 --> 06:59.208
I BETTER REFRIGERATE THIS.

07:09.083 --> 07:10.792
TAKING A LIFE IS ONE THING,

07:10.792 --> 07:13.750
BUT THE CARE AND FEEDING OF IT
IS ANOTHER.

07:13.750 --> 07:17.125
I CAN'T KEEP MY PROBLEM
LOCKED AWAY IN A CABIN FOREVER.

07:20.125 --> 07:21.417
HARRY ALWAYS SAID

07:21.417 --> 07:23.834
THERE WERE PLENTY OF PEOPLE
WHO DESERVED TO DIE,

07:23.834 --> 07:26.250
BUT NO MATTER HOW HARD
I CLOSE MY EYES AND WISH,

07:26.250 --> 07:29.000
DOAKES ISN'T ONE OF THEM.

07:29.000 --> 07:31.458
[ SIGHS ]

07:31.458 --> 07:34.959
HARRY, YOU NEVER PREPARED ME
FOR THIS ONE.

07:34.959 --> 07:37.208
WHAT DO I DO?

07:37.208 --> 07:39.291
WHAT WOULD YOU DO?

07:41.291 --> 07:42.542
GET A DESCRIPTION OF JUAN RYNESS

07:42.542 --> 07:44.125
TO EVERY PATROL UNIT
IN THE CITY,

07:44.125 --> 07:45.542
AND WAKE UP JUDGE MOREHOUSE.

07:45.542 --> 07:47.500
I NEED A WARRANT FOR
RYNESS' APARTMENT IMMEDIATELY.

07:47.500 --> 07:49.291
FISK, MAKE SURE
YOU GET THAT PRINT...

07:49.291 --> 07:50.792
SHE WAS DUMPED?

07:50.792 --> 07:53.291
DEBRA, GET BACK INSIDE THE CAR
LIKE I TOLD YOU.

07:53.291 --> 07:55.583
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ON RADIO ]

07:55.583 --> 07:57.375
BLUNT TRAUMA TO THE HEAD?

07:57.375 --> 08:01.000
I WENT OVER THERE.
NO ONE SAW.

08:01.000 --> 08:03.000
THE BLOW TO THE HEAD
KILLED HER.

08:03.000 --> 08:05.959
SHE TOOK A BRUTAL BEATING
BEFOREHAND.

08:05.959 --> 08:08.166
THE GUY WHO DID THIS
IS AN EVIL BASTARD.

08:08.166 --> 08:10.291
YOU KNOW WHO IT WAS?
OH, YEAH.

08:10.291 --> 08:12.750
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO NAIL HIM
FOR A WHILE.

08:12.750 --> 08:15.709
A PIMP NAMED JUAN RYNESS.
SHE WAS ONE OF HIS GIRLS.

08:15.709 --> 08:17.625
SHE WAS DUMPED, RIGHT?

08:17.625 --> 08:19.542
GET BACK IN THE TRUCK.

08:19.542 --> 08:21.625
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

08:23.792 --> 08:25.625
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

08:27.250 --> 08:30.500
[ KNOCKING CONTINUES ]

08:30.500 --> 08:32.542
[ SIGHS ]

08:43.000 --> 08:44.166
YOU AWAKE?

08:44.166 --> 08:46.458
YOU FOR REAL?

08:46.458 --> 08:48.625
YOU GOT A VISITOR.

08:49.625 --> 08:51.709
COFFEE?

08:54.000 --> 08:57.333
YEAH.
WHY NOT?

09:04.333 --> 09:06.333
I HEARD THE NEWS.
IT'S EVERYWHERE.

09:06.333 --> 09:08.333
SERGEANT DOAKES IS
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER?

09:10.333 --> 09:12.500
THAT'S WHAT THEY'RE SAYING.

09:12.500 --> 09:14.083
I WAS RIGHT ABOUT YOU,
DEXTER.

09:14.083 --> 09:15.583
ARE YOU OKAY?

09:15.583 --> 09:17.917
WHY IS THE FBI
GUARDING YOUR BUILDING?

09:17.917 --> 09:20.291
OH, YOU KNOW
THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT --

09:20.291 --> 09:22.208
ANY EXCUSE TO SPEND MONEY.

09:23.333 --> 09:24.875
MM.

09:24.875 --> 09:26.583
IT'S COLD.

09:26.583 --> 09:28.500
SORRY.

09:28.500 --> 09:31.375
WELL, THERE'S NOTHING BETTER
ON A MUGGY MIAMI MORNING

09:31.375 --> 09:34.875
THAN AN ICED COFFEE,
RIGHT?

09:34.875 --> 09:36.709
[ ICE CUBES RATTLE ]

09:40.041 --> 09:41.875
HOW ARE THE KIDS?

09:41.875 --> 09:45.959
THEY ASKED ABOUT YOU AGAIN.

09:45.959 --> 09:50.125
AND THEY'VE BEEN PRETTY CONFUSED
SINCE WE SPLIT UP.

09:51.959 --> 09:53.709
YEAH. ME TOO.

09:53.709 --> 09:55.834
ARE YOU STILL CONFUSED?

09:55.834 --> 10:01.083
I'M GENERALLY CONFUSED
MOST OF THE TIME...

10:01.083 --> 10:02.875
BUT NOT ABOUT US.

10:04.500 --> 10:05.625
GOOD.

10:08.750 --> 10:09.875
NO.

10:11.166 --> 10:13.000
IT'S NOT GOOD?

10:13.000 --> 10:17.583
NO.
IT'S, UM, GREAT...

10:17.583 --> 10:21.375
TO HAVE THIS CLARITY.

10:22.375 --> 10:24.750
I'M REALLY GLAD
YOU FEEL THAT WAY, DEXTER.

10:24.750 --> 10:27.750
THE KIDS HAVE BEEN THROUGH
SO MUCH LATELY.

10:27.750 --> 10:30.875
WITH PAUL'S DEATH
AND MY MOM MOVING OUT,

10:30.875 --> 10:32.750
I DON'T WANT THEM TO FEEL

10:32.750 --> 10:35.417
LIKE THEY'VE BEEN ABANDONED
BY EVERYONE THEY LOVE.

10:40.500 --> 10:42.583
DOES THIS MEAN
WE'RE DATING AGAIN?

10:45.291 --> 10:48.542
THAT WOULD BE KIND OF FAST,
WOULDN'T IT?

10:48.542 --> 10:52.291
I MEAN, YOU'RE
SO IMPORTANT TO THEM,

10:52.291 --> 10:54.125
AND THEY NEED YOU.

10:54.125 --> 10:58.083
BUT I DON'T KNOW.

10:59.291 --> 11:01.875
I MEAN,
MAYBE WE COULD JUST...

11:01.875 --> 11:03.417
HANG.

11:04.625 --> 11:06.917
LIKE A SLOTH.

11:06.917 --> 11:08.542
I CAN DO THAT.

11:12.166 --> 11:14.333
WELL, IF YOU'RE FREE
ON SATURDAY,

11:14.333 --> 11:16.667
WE'RE GONNA SPEND THE DAY
AT THE BEACH,

11:16.667 --> 11:20.166
AND MAYBE WE COULD ALL
HANG TOGETHER.

11:20.166 --> 11:23.291
A FAMILY OF SLOTHS.

11:24.959 --> 11:26.834
MM.
[ LAUGHS ]

11:26.834 --> 11:29.125
LET ME GET YOU SOME ICE.

11:31.333 --> 11:33.041
I'VE BEEN SELFISH --

11:33.041 --> 11:36.500
ONLY THINKING ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENS TO ME.

11:36.500 --> 11:39.333
BUT IF I WERE EVER REVEALED
AS THE TRUE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER,

11:39.333 --> 11:41.291
RITA AND HER CHILDREN
WOULD BE DESTROYED.

12:01.250 --> 12:03.250
LIEUTENANT?

12:03.250 --> 12:05.000
YES, MORGAN.

12:11.709 --> 12:13.333
I NEED YOU TO TAKE A LOOK
AT THESE.

12:13.333 --> 12:14.834
I KNOW WHAT THEY ARE.

12:16.875 --> 12:18.875
YOU DIDN'T REPORT
THE CALL FROM DOAKES.

12:18.875 --> 12:23.041
YOUR TASK FORCE DOESN'T NEED
MY HELP RAILROADING A GOOD COP.

12:25.875 --> 12:27.875
DOAKES WAS OFFICIALLY
A PERSON OF INTEREST.

12:27.875 --> 12:29.083
NOT REPORTING THAT CALL

12:29.083 --> 12:31.375
COULD BE CONSIDERED
AIDING AND ABETTING.

12:31.375 --> 12:33.375
NONE OF YOU WANTED TO HEAR
WHAT HE HAD TO SAY,

12:33.375 --> 12:34.542
SO I DIDN'T TELL YOU.

12:36.041 --> 12:37.458
WHAT DID  HE HAVE TO SAY?

12:37.458 --> 12:39.542
THAT HE'S INNOCENT.

12:39.542 --> 12:40.959
AND YOU BELIEVE HIM?

12:43.417 --> 12:45.208
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

12:47.417 --> 12:48.750
AND IF HE CALLS AGAIN?

12:48.750 --> 12:50.583
HE WON'T.

12:50.583 --> 12:52.875
AND YOU KNOW THIS?
BECAUSE I KNOW HIM.

12:55.083 --> 12:56.583
I THOUGHT
I KNEW SOMEONE, TOO.

12:56.583 --> 12:58.208
I KNOW HIM.

12:58.208 --> 13:01.333
SO IF LUNDY WANTS TO FLAG ME
TO CAPTAIN MATTHEWS,

13:01.333 --> 13:03.166
YOU TELL HIM
TO GO FOR IT.

13:03.166 --> 13:05.500
BUT JAMES KNOWS
THAT I BELIEVE IN HIM,

13:05.500 --> 13:07.083
SO IT WAS WORTH THE RISK.

13:07.083 --> 13:09.333
TO YOUR JOB?

13:09.333 --> 13:11.041
TO YOUR CAREER?

13:12.583 --> 13:15.291
YOU EVER CARE
ABOUT ANYONE, MORGAN?

13:16.458 --> 13:17.792
YES.

13:20.458 --> 13:22.625
THEN YOU SHOULDN'T
HAVE TO ASK.

13:22.625 --> 13:24.750
'CAUSE WHEN YOU CARE
ABOUT SOMEONE,

13:24.750 --> 13:26.750
YOU DO
WHAT YOU HAVE TO DO.

13:35.625 --> 13:39.041
FOUR DIFFERENT ALIASES --
ALL ISSUED BY THE D.O.D.

13:39.041 --> 13:41.542
DURING DOAKES' STINT
WITH SPECIAL FORCES.

13:41.542 --> 13:44.959
WE'VE ATTACHED THESE NAMES
TO OUR TEMPORARY FELONY WANT,

13:44.959 --> 13:47.542
SO IF HE USES ONE,
WE'LL BE NOTIFIED.

13:47.542 --> 13:49.375
I REMEMBER WHEN LIFE WAS EASY,

13:49.375 --> 13:52.125
WHEN THE ONLY QUESTION I
WORRIED ABOUT WAS "WHO'S NEXT?"

13:52.125 --> 13:55.291
NOW IT'S, "HOW CAN I DODGE
MY PROTECTIVE DETAIL?

13:55.291 --> 13:57.667
WHAT SHOULD I DO
WITH MY HOSTAGE?"

13:57.667 --> 14:00.041
THESE ARE NOT EASY QUESTIONS.

14:00.041 --> 14:02.375
MORGAN, WOULD YOU
BRING US UP TO SPEED

14:02.375 --> 14:05.083
ON THE ANALYSIS
FROM THE BLOOD SLIDES?

14:05.083 --> 14:06.333
OF THE 46 SLIDES,

14:06.333 --> 14:10.083
18 BELONGED TO PREVIOUSLY KNOWN
BUTCHER VICTIMS.

14:10.083 --> 14:11.667
WE'RE STILL RUNNING THE DNA,

14:11.667 --> 14:14.250
BUT WE'VE MATCHED
AN ADDITIONAL 12

14:14.250 --> 14:17.125
WITH FELONS IN THE CRIMINAL
DATABASE, ALL REPORTED MISSING.

14:18.291 --> 14:19.834
WE'LL PROCEED
ON THE ASSUMPTION

14:19.834 --> 14:21.667
THAT THESE 12
WERE BAY HARBOR VICTIMS.

14:21.667 --> 14:24.000
IT'S A FAIR ASSUMPTION.

14:25.166 --> 14:29.041
OFFICER MORGAN, DO YOU HAVE
THE NEW VICTIMS' JACKETS?

14:29.041 --> 14:32.959
SORRY, SIR.
NOT MY RESPONSIBILITY.

14:33.834 --> 14:36.625
THAT'D BE ME.

14:36.625 --> 14:40.959
EACH OF THE 12 HAD AT LEAST
ONE HOMICIDE ON THEIR RECORDS,

14:40.959 --> 14:43.333
AND WE ALL KNOW
HOW THE BUTCHER LOVES A KILLER.

14:43.333 --> 14:46.834
WE'RE CHECKING INTO
THEIR LAST KNOWN WHEREABOUTS

14:46.834 --> 14:48.834
AND ANY CONNECTION
THAT THEIR CRIMINAL CASES

14:48.834 --> 14:50.875
MAY HAVE HAD
WITH SERGEANT DOAKES.

14:50.875 --> 14:54.125
FORENSICS, EXPECT A STEADY
STREAM OF EVIDENCE SEIZED

14:54.125 --> 14:57.542
FROM OUR SUSPECT'S APARTMENT
OVER THE NEXT FEW HOURS.

14:57.542 --> 14:58.959
YOU'RE LOOKING
FOR ANY TRACE EVIDENCE

14:58.959 --> 15:00.208
THAT COULD CONNECT HIM
TO THESE VICTIMS.

15:00.208 --> 15:02.959
THE REST OF YOU HAVE
YOUR ASSIGNMENTS.

15:02.959 --> 15:04.834
LET'S BRING HIM IN, FOLKS.

15:09.458 --> 15:10.834
SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY?

15:10.834 --> 15:13.417
DEXTER,
IS YOUR SISTER ALL RIGHT?

15:13.417 --> 15:15.500
I WOULDN'T KNOW.

15:15.500 --> 15:18.375
BUT I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT MY PROTECTIVE DETAIL.

15:21.750 --> 15:25.375
ANGEL, I HEAR YOU HAVE
12 NEW BUTCHER VICTIMS.

15:25.375 --> 15:26.500
POTENTIAL VICTIMS.

15:26.500 --> 15:28.375
YOU GOT NAMES?

15:31.250 --> 15:33.875
MIND IF I KEEP THIS?

15:33.875 --> 15:36.125
WE'RE ALL WORKING
TOGETHER NOW.

15:36.125 --> 15:38.583
WHY?
YOU GOT AN ANGLE ON DOAKES?

15:42.500 --> 15:44.542
[ METAL RATTLING ]

15:53.625 --> 15:57.041
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

16:03.458 --> 16:06.583
OH, YEAH.
THAT'S GOOD.

16:06.583 --> 16:09.291
THAT'S REAL GOOD.

16:09.291 --> 16:10.792
THIS IS A WASTE OF TIME.

16:10.792 --> 16:12.125
IF DOAKES IS THE BUTCHER,

16:12.125 --> 16:14.166
WE'RE NOT GONNA FIND
TRACE EVIDENCE ON HIS CLOTHES.

16:14.166 --> 16:16.917
THE GUY WE'RE AFTER
IS WAY TOO CAREFUL FOR THAT.

16:16.917 --> 16:19.500
I HAVE TO AGREE
WITH YOU THERE.

16:20.875 --> 16:22.959
YOU THINK
IT COULD BE DOAKES?

16:25.125 --> 16:28.083
IT'S NOT ABOUT WHAT I THINK.
IT'S ALL ABOUT THE EVIDENCE.

16:28.083 --> 16:29.458
[ SIGHS ]

16:29.458 --> 16:32.875
ALL THOSE TIMES
YOU CALLED ME "LAB GEEK,"

16:32.875 --> 16:35.458
"FAIRY WINKLE,"
"DONKEY FLUFFER"...

16:35.458 --> 16:36.625
[ SIGHS ]

16:36.625 --> 16:39.000
...I'M JUST GLAD I TOOK IT
LYING DOWN, YOU KNOW?

16:39.000 --> 16:40.458
[ DOOR OPENS ]

16:40.458 --> 16:42.625
WHAT THE FUCK, DEX?

16:42.625 --> 16:44.000
WHAT WHICH FUCK?

16:44.000 --> 16:46.333
YOU TOLD LUNDY TO PULL
YOUR PROTECTIVE DETAIL?

16:46.333 --> 16:48.375
OH, SHE'S GONNA HIT YOU,
ISN'T SHE?

16:48.375 --> 16:50.667
SHE'S GONNA HIT SOMEONE IF YOU
DON'T GET THE FUCK OUT OF HERE.

16:50.667 --> 16:54.291
HAIR-PULLING MAY NOT BE MANLY,
BUT IT'S VERY EFFECTIVE.

16:59.041 --> 17:01.208
DOAKES FUCKING
HATES YOU, DEX.

17:01.208 --> 17:04.250
NO DOUBT ABOUT THAT.
AND HE'S A TRAINED KILLER.

17:04.250 --> 17:06.166
IF HE WANTED ME DEAD,
IT WOULD HAVE HAPPENED BY NOW.

17:06.166 --> 17:07.709
IS THAT SUPPOSED TO BE
REASSURING?

17:07.709 --> 17:09.834
DOAKES IS A LOT OF THINGS,
BUT HE'S NOT AN IDIOT.

17:09.834 --> 17:12.125
HE WON'T COME OUT OF THE SHADOWS
BECAUSE OF A GRUDGE.

17:12.125 --> 17:14.500
RIGHT.

17:14.500 --> 17:17.000
'CAUSE SERIAL KILLERS
ARE SO PRACTICAL.

17:17.000 --> 17:19.208
ACTUALLY, THEY ARE.

17:19.208 --> 17:22.500
DEB, I'M SAFER WITH
LUNDY'S TROOPS HUNTING DOAKES

17:22.500 --> 17:23.542
THAN BABYSITTING ME.

17:23.542 --> 17:24.500
LUNDY AGREES.

17:24.500 --> 17:26.291
THAT'S 'CAUSE LUNDY
DOESN'T GIVE A SHIT!

17:26.291 --> 17:29.959
ALL HE CARES ABOUT IS SOLVING
THIS CASE AND MOVING ON!

17:29.959 --> 17:32.041
I THOUGHT HE WAS THE GUY
YOU COULD COUNT ON.

17:34.625 --> 17:37.500
YOU ARE THE ONLY ONE
I CAN COUNT ON, JACKASS.

17:39.417 --> 17:41.333
DEB.
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

17:41.333 --> 17:43.500
GOT TO GIVE DEB CREDIT
FOR ONE THING --

17:43.500 --> 17:46.417
SHE KNOWS HOW TO EXPRESS
HER FEELINGS.

17:47.750 --> 17:49.625
IF I WAS CONVICTED
AS THE BUTCHER,

17:49.625 --> 17:51.542
SHE'D PROBABLY EXPLODE.

17:51.542 --> 17:54.667
IT'D BE A WASTE
OF A PERFECTLY GOOD COP...

17:54.667 --> 17:56.333
AND SISTER.

17:56.333 --> 17:57.333
[ CAR ALARM BEEPS ]

17:57.333 --> 18:00.500
THIS ISN'T JUST ABOUT ME
ANYMORE.

18:00.500 --> 18:03.917
IT'S ABOUT DEB AND RITA
AND THE KIDS.

18:03.917 --> 18:06.709
I HAVE ONLY ONE CHOICE
FOR DOAKES.

18:17.834 --> 18:19.250
SHIT.

18:23.542 --> 18:25.542
ALL RIGHT.

18:37.917 --> 18:39.208
YES.

18:44.959 --> 18:48.083
[ VEHICLE APPROACHING ]

19:03.709 --> 19:05.125
[ BAG UNZIPS ]

19:14.291 --> 19:17.125
NO REASON
FOR YOU TO SUFFER.

19:19.250 --> 19:20.917
MM.

19:23.750 --> 19:25.875
YOU COME TO A DECISION?

19:25.875 --> 19:28.166
YES, BUT I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE GONNA LIKE IT.

19:35.834 --> 19:37.291
SO THIS IS THE WAY IT ENDS.

19:39.333 --> 19:42.542
REGARDLESS OF
HOW WE GOT HERE,

19:42.542 --> 19:45.333
ONE OF THE TWO KILLERS
IN THIS CABIN HAS TO GO AWAY.

19:45.333 --> 19:46.625
I AM NOT A KILLER.

19:46.625 --> 19:48.834
RIGHT.

19:48.834 --> 19:51.333
IN TERMS OF WHO GOES,

19:51.333 --> 19:53.834
IT BOILED DOWN TO
A PHILOSOPHICAL QUESTION --

19:53.834 --> 19:58.333
WHICH ONE OF US
HAS MORE INHERENT WORTH?

19:58.333 --> 20:01.166
[ Laughing ] I KNOW
YOU'RE FUCKING KIDDING ME.

20:01.166 --> 20:03.792
FIRST I CONSIDERED
OUR VALUE TO THE COMMUNITY.

20:03.792 --> 20:06.625
THAT WAS A WASH.

20:06.625 --> 20:08.917
WE'RE BOTH
LOYAL CIVIL SERVANTS.

20:08.917 --> 20:11.125
WE WORK HARD
TO KEEP THE CITY CLEAN.

20:11.125 --> 20:13.041
YOU CUT PEOPLE UP
INTO LITTLE PIECES.

20:13.041 --> 20:17.417
THEN I LOOKED
AT OUR PERSONAL LIVES.

20:17.417 --> 20:20.250
AND, WELL...

20:20.250 --> 20:23.750
THAT'S WHERE THE DIFFERENCES
BECAME CLEARER.

20:23.750 --> 20:26.041
STRANGE AS IT MAY SEEM,

20:26.041 --> 20:28.834
I HAVE PEOPLE
WHO DEPEND ON ME.

20:28.834 --> 20:33.375
THEY WOULD BE DEVASTATED
IF THEY FOUND OUT WHAT I DO.

20:33.375 --> 20:35.959
YOU, SERGEANT,

20:35.959 --> 20:39.083
YOU'RE MORE OF A LONE WOLF --
EASIER TO PUT DOWN.

20:39.083 --> 20:41.083
NO ONE IN THE PACK
TO MISS YOU.

20:41.083 --> 20:43.041
FUCK YOU.

20:43.041 --> 20:44.291
FUCK YOU, MORGAN.
I HAVE A FAMILY.

20:44.291 --> 20:45.959
I HAVE MY MOTHER
AND MY SISTERS.

20:45.959 --> 20:47.667
WHO YOU NEVER VISIT.

20:52.875 --> 20:55.250
IT PUTS A PIT
IN MY STOMACH

20:55.250 --> 20:59.417
THAT I CAN
ONLY INTERPRET AS...

20:59.417 --> 21:01.709
SADNESS.

21:03.458 --> 21:05.417
IF YOU HAD
A PERSONAL LIFE,

21:05.417 --> 21:07.083
YOU MIGHT NOT HAVE MADE ME
YOUR OBSESSION,

21:07.083 --> 21:10.917
AND WE WOULDN'T
BE HERE RIGHT NOW.

21:10.917 --> 21:12.375
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]

21:15.792 --> 21:17.750
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

21:24.000 --> 21:27.250
SERGEANT,
WHY WOULD YOU HIDE

21:27.250 --> 21:30.208
A DEAD DRUG DEALER'S
CELLPHONE FROM ME?

21:30.208 --> 21:32.417
YOU WORKING ON
AN EXIT STRATEGY?

21:32.417 --> 21:34.417
I'M AFRAID
THAT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

21:37.000 --> 21:39.500
IF YOU WANT TO
BRING ME DOWN, MORGAN,

21:39.500 --> 21:42.709
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO OPEN
THIS GODDAMN CAGE FIRST.

21:42.709 --> 21:45.500
SO COME ON.
BRING IT.

21:45.500 --> 21:49.291
I ALREADY DID.
YOU JUST DIDN'T KNOW IT.

21:54.834 --> 21:57.458
MOTHER FUCK...

21:57.458 --> 21:58.792
THE SEDATIVE WORKS FAST.

21:58.792 --> 22:01.083
IT'S PROBABLY BEST
JUST TO GO WITH IT.

22:01.083 --> 22:03.625
[ BREATHING SHALLOWLY ]

22:03.625 --> 22:05.458
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:05.458 --> 22:07.291
YOU THINK YOU'RE A FUCKING HERO,
DON'T YOU?

22:07.291 --> 22:09.291
CLEANING UP
THE FUCKING STREETS.

22:09.291 --> 22:11.917
[ LAUGHS ]
YOUR OLD MAN WOULD BE PROUD.

22:14.041 --> 22:15.875
MY OLD MAN WAS  PROUD.

22:18.333 --> 22:19.709
HE KNEW?

22:19.709 --> 22:21.583
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:21.583 --> 22:24.542
HE REALLY WAS
A FUCKING WHACK JOB.

22:24.542 --> 22:28.000
NAME-CALLING
AT THIS JUNCTURE?

22:28.000 --> 22:30.208
WHAT'S THE POINT?

22:30.208 --> 22:32.709
BESIDES, MY FATHER WAS
A LEGEND ON THE FORCE.

22:32.709 --> 22:34.875
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?

22:34.875 --> 22:36.834
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:36.834 --> 22:39.458
THEY NEVER TOLD YOU.

22:41.542 --> 22:43.375
TOLD ME?
TOLD ME WHAT?

22:44.750 --> 22:46.458
HEY!

22:46.458 --> 22:48.917
WHAT ABOUT MY FATHER?

22:48.917 --> 22:52.166
WHAT ABOUT MY FATHER?

22:58.041 --> 23:00.500
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
OH.

23:04.166 --> 23:05.542
A MISSED CALL.

23:05.542 --> 23:08.542
IF IT'S DEXTER,
TELL HIM TO COME OVER.

23:13.709 --> 23:15.500
I HAVE AURI ON SATURDAY.

23:15.500 --> 23:17.041
AURI?
WHAT'S AN AURI?

23:17.041 --> 23:18.542
IT'S MY LITTLE GIRL.

23:18.542 --> 23:21.709
MY EX NEVER LETS ME SEE HER
ON THE WEEKENDS,

23:21.709 --> 23:23.750
BUT SOMETHING CAME UP.

23:23.750 --> 23:26.000
I HAVE HER ALL DAY
ON SATURDAY.

23:26.000 --> 23:29.333
MM. DELIGHTFUL.

23:29.333 --> 23:32.542
BUT TONIGHT
YOU BELONG TO ME...

23:32.542 --> 23:34.500
YES.

23:34.500 --> 23:36.041
...AND MY WALLS.

23:36.041 --> 23:37.875
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:38.875 --> 23:40.333
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

23:40.333 --> 23:42.291
DOAKES SAID
I HAD TWO CHOICES --

23:42.291 --> 23:45.750
KILL HIM OR LET HIM GO.

23:45.750 --> 23:48.917
BUT HE NEGLECTED TO LOOK BEHIND
DOOR NUMBER THREE --

23:48.917 --> 23:51.834
HAND HIM OVER
TO THE FBI GIFT-WRAPPED.

23:51.834 --> 23:53.792
I DON'T NEED DOAKES DEAD.

23:53.792 --> 23:57.083
I JUST NEED HIS FINGERPRINTS
TO COMPLETE MY FRAME JOB.

24:05.458 --> 24:08.041
ALMOST FORGOT.

24:12.125 --> 24:14.625
ONE NEEDS SMALL COMFORTS.

24:34.166 --> 24:37.000
EVERY SATURDAY,
BEGINNING DIVE CLASSES

24:37.000 --> 24:40.208
PRACTICE UNDERWATER SKILLS
BESIDE THIS DOCK.

24:40.208 --> 24:44.166
TOMORROW THEY'LL FIND
A MORBID LITTLE SURPRISE.

24:47.166 --> 24:49.125
WHEN THE FEDS RECEIVE
THESE KILL TOOLS

24:49.125 --> 24:51.000
WITH THEIR SUSPECT'S PRINTS
ON THEM,

24:51.000 --> 24:52.542
THE ONLY THREAT TO ME WILL BE

24:52.542 --> 24:55.583
THE INANE RANTS
OF A MURDEROUS MADMAN.

25:00.208 --> 25:02.041
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

25:02.041 --> 25:04.625
SO CLOSE, I CAN FEEL IT.

25:14.000 --> 25:17.083
THIS TRAGIC TALE MIGHT
STILL END IN DOAKES' DEMISE,

25:17.083 --> 25:19.458
BUT NOT BY MY HANDS.

25:19.458 --> 25:22.792
HARRY'S LEGACY
WILL REMAIN INTACT.

25:22.792 --> 25:24.250
HARRY...

25:24.250 --> 25:28.208
WHY IN THE HELL DID DOAKES
HAVE TO BRING UP HARRY?

25:33.291 --> 25:35.875
[ Laughing ]
COME ON.

25:35.875 --> 25:37.041
[ LAUGHS ]

25:37.041 --> 25:38.667
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

25:38.667 --> 25:40.333
YOU JUST CUT THE CAKE,
SWEETHEART.

25:40.333 --> 25:42.625
I'LL SEE WHO IT IS.

25:44.417 --> 25:47.125
TOM. THIS IS A SURPRISE.
COME ON IN.

25:47.125 --> 25:48.709
OH, THANKS.

25:48.709 --> 25:51.709
SWEETHEART, CUT
THE LIEUTENANT A SLICE.

25:51.709 --> 25:53.250
IT'S HER BIRTHDAY.

25:53.250 --> 25:55.500
OH!
WELL, HAPPY BIRTHDAY, HON.

25:55.500 --> 25:57.750
BUT NO CAKE FOR ME, THANKS.

25:57.750 --> 26:00.250
CAN I TALK TO YOU
IN PRIVATE FOR A SECOND?
SURE.

26:00.250 --> 26:01.709
SAVE ME AN END PIECE.

26:05.625 --> 26:08.041
Harry:
GOD DAMN IT!

26:08.041 --> 26:09.583
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

26:09.583 --> 26:13.750
RYNESS IS GONNA WALK
BECAUSE OF A GODDAMN TYPO?!

26:13.750 --> 26:15.500
FAULTY WARRANT, HARRY.
THERE'S NOTHING WE CAN DO.

26:15.500 --> 26:17.166
THIS IS BULLSHIT!
HARRY!

26:18.375 --> 26:19.792
NOW, LOOK, DON'T WORRY.

26:19.792 --> 26:22.458
RYNESS WILL MAKE
ANOTHER MISTAKE.
YEAH, RIGHT.

26:22.458 --> 26:24.875
WE JUST GOT WAIT FOR HIM
TO KILL ANOTHER GIRL!

26:24.875 --> 26:26.875
SORRY.

26:36.583 --> 26:38.625
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, KIDDO.

26:42.083 --> 26:44.458
I'LL GET
THE VACUUM CLEANER.

26:54.500 --> 26:55.875
YOU OKAY, DAD?

26:59.500 --> 27:02.208
I DID THE RIGHT THING
IN TRAINING YOU.

27:02.208 --> 27:04.500
THIS JUST PROVES IT.

27:04.500 --> 27:07.500
I DID THE RIGHT THING.

27:13.000 --> 27:14.792
DEBRA.

27:14.792 --> 27:16.291
WILL YOU WAIT?

27:16.291 --> 27:18.709
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

27:18.709 --> 27:20.583
NOTHING, ACCORDING TO YOU.

27:20.583 --> 27:22.959
SO I SAID SOMETHING?

27:22.959 --> 27:26.208
ONLY THAT THIS RELATIONSHIP
HAS AN EXPIRATION DATE.

27:26.208 --> 27:30.125
IF YOU WANT TO WRITE IT OFF
BEFORE IT EVEN BEGINS, GO AHEAD.

27:30.125 --> 27:31.291
WHEN DID I SAY THAT?

27:31.291 --> 27:34.208
YESTERDAY MORNING, YOU SAID,
"WHEN THE CASE ENDS, WE END."

27:34.208 --> 27:36.166
I'M PARAPHRASING.

27:36.166 --> 27:40.458
DEBRA, I THOUGHT YOU UNDERSTOOD
WHEN WE GOT INVOLVED.

27:40.458 --> 27:42.500
I TRACK KILLERS.
THAT'S WHAT I DO.

27:42.500 --> 27:45.208
THEY TEND TO MOVE AROUND.
I KNOW THAT.

27:45.208 --> 27:47.333
THEN I'M NOT SURE

27:47.333 --> 27:49.792
WHAT YOU THOUGHT WOULD HAPPEN
WHEN THE CASE ENDED.

27:51.875 --> 27:54.208
HONESTLY, I HADN'T
THOUGHT ABOUT IT,

27:54.208 --> 27:57.166
BUT IT LOOKS LIKE YOU HAVE,
SO NOW I KNOW.

27:57.166 --> 27:59.291
CONSIDER ME INFORMED.

28:02.667 --> 28:04.875
[ SIGHS ]

28:08.000 --> 28:09.792
ONE.

28:09.792 --> 28:12.875
HOW COME THERE'S NEVER A CIRCUS
WHEN YOU NEED ONE?

28:12.875 --> 28:14.250
I DON'T KNOW.

28:14.250 --> 28:17.250
I'M NOT SURE I'VE EVER FELT
THAT PARTICULAR NEED.

28:17.250 --> 28:19.667
HELP ME OUT HERE.

28:19.667 --> 28:21.041
WHAT DOES A
7-YEAR-OLD GIRL LIKE?

28:21.041 --> 28:23.542
ASTOR LIKES CNN.

28:23.542 --> 28:25.750
YEAH.
THAT'S NOT GONNA FLY.

28:25.750 --> 28:28.500
I GOT AURI
ALL DAY ON SATURDAY.

28:28.500 --> 28:31.542
I WANT TO DO SOMETHING FUN --
IDEALLY, A LOT MORE FUN

28:31.542 --> 28:33.834
THAN THE STUFF
HER MOTHER DOES WITH HER.

28:33.834 --> 28:36.291
IT'S REALLY NOT THAT HARD
TO ENTERTAIN A KID.

28:36.291 --> 28:38.917
RITA AND I ARE TAKING HERS
TO THE BEACH ON SATURDAY.

28:38.917 --> 28:40.875
SEE, NOW,
THAT SOUNDS PERFECT.

28:40.875 --> 28:42.875
IT'D BE GREAT
IF WE COULD TAG ALONG.

28:44.375 --> 28:46.542
OH, UH...

28:46.542 --> 28:48.041
SURE, I GUESS.

28:48.041 --> 28:50.166
WE'LL BE THERE
ALL AFTERNOON.

28:52.792 --> 28:54.375
SORRY, BUT WHAT'S
WITH THE HIGHLIGHTS?

28:54.375 --> 28:58.125
I WAS HELPING LILA
PAINT HER LOFT LAST NIGHT.

28:58.125 --> 29:00.583
RED --
THE COLOR OF PASIóN.

29:00.583 --> 29:03.417
YEAH.
ABOUT LILA.

29:03.417 --> 29:05.625
UH, IT'S PROBABLY
BETTER FOR EVERYONE

29:05.625 --> 29:08.000
IF SHE DOESN'T COME ALONG
ON SATURDAY.

29:08.000 --> 29:10.041
BRO, I'M NOT STUPID.

29:10.041 --> 29:13.917
LILA IS LIKE
MY AFTER-HOURS PROJECT.

29:13.917 --> 29:16.834
BESIDES, SHE SHOULD STAY OFF
THE BEACH WITH SKIN LIKE THAT.

29:16.834 --> 29:20.417
LIKE A PERFECT
PORCELAIN DOLL.

29:20.417 --> 29:24.208
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]

29:24.208 --> 29:27.458
"PAID 4 MY LIFT TICKET.
WHERE'S MY SNOW?

29:27.458 --> 29:29.917
DON'T MAKE ME COME AFTER U."

29:29.917 --> 29:32.834
SOUNDS LIKE MR. HARLOW IS
NOT ONLY A MASTER OF METAPHOR,

29:32.834 --> 29:35.250
BUT ALSO INCLINED TOWARD
VIOLENT CONFRONTATION.

29:35.250 --> 29:38.208
BETTER FIND OUT WHO HE IS IN
CASE I HAVE TO DEAL WITH HIM.

29:41.709 --> 29:43.333
ARMED WITH A PHONE NUMBER,

29:43.333 --> 29:46.291
OBTAINING THE MYSTERIOUS
TEXT-MESSENGER'S I.D.

29:46.291 --> 29:48.542
WASN'T TOO HARD,
BUT IS HE A THREAT?

29:50.583 --> 29:54.583
"CHRISTOPHER HARLOW --
KNOWN ALIAS FOR JOSE GARZA.

29:54.583 --> 29:57.500
"NARCOTICS, ARMED ROBBERY,

29:57.500 --> 30:00.417
"AND CURRENTLY A FUGITIVE
FROM JUSTICE FOR MURDER.

30:00.417 --> 30:02.792
APPROACH WITH CAUTION."

30:14.917 --> 30:18.542
THIS GUY COULD BE TROUBLE
IF HE HAS KNOWLEDGE

30:18.542 --> 30:21.333
OF A CERTAIN CABIN
IN THE EVERGLADES.

30:21.333 --> 30:23.333
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

30:26.333 --> 30:28.875
I'M SAFE.

30:28.875 --> 30:30.458
HAPPY TRAILS, HARLOW.

30:42.333 --> 30:43.834
DEB?
[ GASPS ]

30:43.834 --> 30:45.834
FUCK!
SNEAK MUCH?

30:45.834 --> 30:48.500
SORRY.
I WANTED TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

30:48.500 --> 30:51.625
THAT IS SOME BIG HAIR.

30:51.625 --> 30:54.417
HARD TO BELIEVE
HE'S OUR GUY.

30:54.417 --> 30:58.250
AMAZING HOW EASY IT IS TO HIDE
WHO YOU ARE FROM PEOPLE, HUH?

30:58.250 --> 30:59.834
NOT THAT EASY.

31:01.792 --> 31:05.667
I WAS THINKING ABOUT
YOUR BIRTHDAY.

31:05.667 --> 31:07.792
YOU GOT LIKE THREE MONTHS.

31:07.792 --> 31:09.500
JUST GET ME A GIFT CERTIFICATE
AT AMAZON.

31:09.500 --> 31:13.208
GOOD TO KNOW, BUT THE BIRTHDAY
I WAS THINKING ABOUT WAS...

31:13.208 --> 31:15.125
WHEN DAD THREW
THE BEER BOTTLE.

31:17.542 --> 31:20.000
JESUS.

31:20.000 --> 31:22.083
OUT OF THE BLUE, DEX.
WHAT BROUGHT THAT UP?

31:24.250 --> 31:28.000
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
HARRY'S BEEN ON MY MIND LATELY.

31:28.000 --> 31:30.750
I WAS TRYING TO REMEMBER...

31:30.750 --> 31:33.000
MATTHEWS CAME OVER
THAT NIGHT, RIGHT?

31:33.000 --> 31:35.458
YEAH.

31:35.458 --> 31:37.709
HE AND DAD
GOT IN A FIGHT.

31:37.709 --> 31:39.625
I ENDED UP WIPING BEER
OFF THE WALLS.

31:39.625 --> 31:41.000
HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME.

31:43.083 --> 31:46.792
A KILLER WENT FREE.
THAT WOULD UPSET ANY COP, RIGHT?

31:46.792 --> 31:48.709
NOTHING WEIRD ABOUT THAT.

31:48.709 --> 31:49.959
NO, IT WASN'T WEIRD.

31:49.959 --> 31:52.375
IT WAS JUST ANOTHER EXAMPLE
OF DAD'S PRIORITIES.

31:52.375 --> 31:54.875
KIDS VERSUS CASE --
CASE ALWAYS WON.

31:56.417 --> 31:59.291
DID HE SAY ANYTHING ELSE
ABOUT IT TO YOU?

32:00.333 --> 32:01.875
RIGHT.

32:01.875 --> 32:04.834
DAD SITTING DOWN WITH ME
TO HAVE A HEART-TO-HEART.

32:04.834 --> 32:06.625
NOT THAT I DIDN'T WANT TO.

32:09.291 --> 32:11.208
MAYBE YOU SHOULD HAVE
TOLD HIM THAT.

32:11.208 --> 32:12.125
YEAH.

32:13.875 --> 32:15.625
MAYBE.

32:15.625 --> 32:17.417
DEB HAD IT ROUGH.

32:17.417 --> 32:20.875
HARRY HAD HIS HANDS FULL
TEACHING ME A TRADE.

32:22.500 --> 32:25.125
BUT WAS THERE SOMETHING ELSE
GOING ON WITH HIM,

32:25.125 --> 32:27.834
OR WAS DOAKES
JUST TRYING TO SHAKE ME UP?

32:27.834 --> 32:30.375
I NEED TO KNOW
IF THERE'S MORE TO THE STORY.

32:30.375 --> 32:32.125
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

32:38.333 --> 32:41.917
THERE'S A COMPLICATION
I DON'T NEED.

32:41.917 --> 32:44.333
HEY, BABY,
WHAT BRINGS YOU BACK?

32:44.333 --> 32:46.583
I HAVE TWO MORE WALLS
AT HOME

32:46.583 --> 32:49.208
WAITING FOR YOUR EXPERTISE
AS A PAINTER.

32:49.208 --> 32:52.959
OH, THERE'S NOTHING
I'D LIKE TO DO MORE, BUT...

32:52.959 --> 32:55.500
BUT WHAT, DARLING?

32:55.500 --> 32:57.041
I'M PICKING UP AURI,
REMEMBER?

32:57.041 --> 33:00.083
WE'RE MEETING DEXTER
AND RITA AT THE BEACH.

33:00.083 --> 33:03.458
YOU KNOW, I HAVE A FRIEND
AT MIAMI ART MUSEUM --

33:03.458 --> 33:05.959
TEACHES AN INCREDIBLE
CHILDREN'S CLASS.

33:05.959 --> 33:07.333
AIR-CONDITIONED.

33:07.333 --> 33:09.417
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:09.417 --> 33:11.333
YOU COULD BRING THE WHOLE GANG
IF YOU LIKE.

33:14.125 --> 33:16.166
YOU MIND IF I TAKE
A RAIN CHECK?

33:16.166 --> 33:18.625
YOU KNOW,
WITH YOUR HISTORY WITH DEXTER,

33:18.625 --> 33:20.417
IT MIGHT BE
A LITTLE AWKWARD.

33:20.417 --> 33:22.500
HE'S TRYING TO
WORK THINGS OUT WITH RITA.

33:24.834 --> 33:27.000
OH, IS HE, NOW?

33:27.917 --> 33:32.458
WELL, YOU HAVE A GREAT DAY.

33:32.458 --> 33:36.000
AND, UM, WATCH OUT
FOR THOSE SAND FLEAS.

33:38.875 --> 33:42.291
DAMN.
SHE BETTER BE WORTH IT.

33:57.959 --> 34:01.458
[ DOOR CLOSES, LOCK CLICKS ]

34:08.083 --> 34:09.917
WHAT WAS THAT SHIT
LAST NIGHT?

34:09.917 --> 34:12.083
SOME KIND OF FUCKING
SCARE TACTIC?

34:12.083 --> 34:15.041
YOU SAID SOMETHING BEFORE
YOU PASSED OUT ABOUT MY FATHER.

34:15.041 --> 34:16.208
WHAT WAS IT?

34:16.208 --> 34:17.709
I DON'T KNOW.
WHAT WAS IT?

34:17.709 --> 34:19.542
I WAS KIND OF DRUGGED
AT THE TIME.

34:22.417 --> 34:23.959
DON'T TEST ME, SERGEANT.

34:23.959 --> 34:26.500
I COULD HAVE KILLED YOU.

34:26.500 --> 34:28.875
I DIDN'T.

34:28.875 --> 34:32.125
YOU DIDN'T
BECAUSE YOU CAN'T.

34:32.125 --> 34:35.166
I'VE HAD TIME TO THINK
ABOUT THIS, MORGAN.

34:35.166 --> 34:38.542
I DON'T FIT THAT CODE
YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT, DO I?

34:40.750 --> 34:43.333
AT FIRST, I THOUGHT THE BUTCHER
ONLY WENT AFTER CRIMINALS

34:43.333 --> 34:45.500
BECAUSE NOBODY GIVES A GODDAMN
WHAT HAPPENS TO THEM,

34:45.500 --> 34:47.083
BUT NOW...

34:47.083 --> 34:48.959
NOW I THINK
YOU GOT A CONSCIENCE.

34:48.959 --> 34:52.250
OF COURSE
I HAVE A CONSCIENCE.

34:52.250 --> 34:54.458
I LEFT YOU A PLACE TO SHIT,
DIDN'T I?

35:02.417 --> 35:04.542
IT'S A SMALL CONSCIENCE.

35:04.542 --> 35:06.250
YOU'RE ACTUALLY ANGRY.

35:06.250 --> 35:08.875
I'VE NEVER SEEN YOU ANGRY.
THIS IS GOOD.

35:08.875 --> 35:11.792
I MIGHT LIVE TO SEE THE OUTSIDE
OF THIS GODDAMN CABIN AFTER ALL.

35:11.792 --> 35:13.125
WHAT'D YOU SAY
ABOUT HARRY?

35:13.125 --> 35:15.041
I BELIEVE THE WORDS "WHACK JOB"
WERE INVOLVED.

35:15.041 --> 35:16.250
OH, YEAH.

35:18.125 --> 35:20.333
IS THAT WHAT YOU'RE
WORRIED ABOUT, MAN?

35:20.333 --> 35:24.458
I GUESS IT WOULD BOTHER ME, TOO,
IF IT WERE MY OLD MAN.

35:24.458 --> 35:26.125
SERGEANT.

35:27.125 --> 35:28.834
OKAY.
WHAT THE FUCK?

35:31.291 --> 35:35.083
YOU KNOW HOW I'VE BEEN LOOKING
INTO YOUR PAST, RIGHT?

35:35.083 --> 35:38.291
THAT'S WHY
YOU'RE IN A CAGE.

35:38.291 --> 35:41.166
I FOUND SOMETHING
I WASN'T SUPPOSED TO SEE.

35:42.458 --> 35:43.959
IT'S ABOUT
YOUR FATHER'S DEATH.

35:43.959 --> 35:46.208
HEART DISEASE --
BIG MYSTERY.

35:46.208 --> 35:49.166
NO, THE MYSTERY'S
BIGGER THAN THAT.

35:49.166 --> 35:52.291
AND SOMEONE UP HIGH
DIDN'T WANT IT SOLVED.

35:55.125 --> 35:56.750
YOU'RE LYING.

35:58.041 --> 36:00.834
IT WAS BURIED DEEP,
BUT IT WAS THERE.

36:03.375 --> 36:04.917
WHAT  WAS THERE?

36:09.625 --> 36:13.667
HOW ABOUT WE GO OUTSIDE
AND TALK ABOUT THIS, MAN?

36:13.667 --> 36:15.375
I COULD USE SOME AIR.

36:15.375 --> 36:17.667
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

36:17.667 --> 36:19.125
NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

36:19.125 --> 36:23.041
YEAH, WELL,
THEN THE MYSTERY REMAINS.

36:33.250 --> 36:35.875
I'M SURE SPECIAL OPS TAUGHT YOU
TO RATTLE YOUR CAPTOR,

36:35.875 --> 36:37.625
BUT I SHOULD WARN YOU,
SERGEANT.

36:37.625 --> 36:40.959
YOU CAN'T PLAY
ON MY FEELINGS.

36:42.166 --> 36:44.166
I DON'T HAVE ANY.

36:44.166 --> 36:47.291
OH, REALLY?

36:47.291 --> 36:49.333
WHO'S LYING NOW?

36:58.750 --> 37:01.875
SIT DOWN.
THAT'S IT.

37:07.208 --> 37:09.959
WELL...

37:09.959 --> 37:12.083
HELLO, DEXTER.
CAPTAIN.

37:12.083 --> 37:15.417
PLEASE. I'M A CIVILIAN TODAY.
CALL ME TOM.

37:15.417 --> 37:18.083
YOU START YOUR ROUND YET?

37:19.375 --> 37:23.625
I'M AFRAID BAYSHORE IS
A LITTLE OUTSIDE MY PAY SCALE.

37:23.625 --> 37:26.834
SO, WHAT BRINGS YOU ALL THE WAY
OUT HERE ON A SATURDAY MORNING?

37:28.333 --> 37:30.083
I WANT TO KNOW IF THERE WAS
ANYTHING UNUSUAL

37:30.083 --> 37:32.834
ABOUT MY FATHER'S DEATH.

37:34.291 --> 37:37.375
UH, GO ON AHEAD.
I'LL CATCH UP.

37:40.375 --> 37:43.041
HIS HEART GAVE OUT.
YOU KNOW THAT.

37:43.041 --> 37:45.250
I HEARD
THERE WAS MORE TO IT.

37:45.250 --> 37:46.542
FROM WHOM?

37:46.542 --> 37:48.875
DOES IT MATTER?

37:53.083 --> 37:55.959
I GUESS IT WAS INEVITABLE YOU'D
FIND OUT ONE OF THESE DAYS.

37:55.959 --> 37:58.750
YOU KNOW, HARRY
WAS A GOOD FRIEND.

37:58.750 --> 38:01.208
HE WAS A GREAT COP.

38:01.208 --> 38:03.417
BUT, UM...

38:03.417 --> 38:05.500
IT'S A TOUGH JOB.

38:05.500 --> 38:07.458
IT CAN WEAR ON
EVEN THE BEST OF US.

38:07.458 --> 38:10.375
MY FATHER WAS ALWAYS
FIRMLY IN CONTROL.

38:10.375 --> 38:15.125
THAT HE WAS,
BUT TOWARDS THE END...

38:15.125 --> 38:17.250
LOOK, DEXTER.

38:17.250 --> 38:20.291
THE SYSTEM
DOESN'T ALWAYS WORK.

38:20.291 --> 38:22.500
SOMETIMES THEY GET AWAY.
YOU KNOW THAT.

38:22.500 --> 38:27.333
AND THAT JUST GOT HARDER AND
HARDER FOR HARRY TO DEAL WITH.

38:27.333 --> 38:30.750
I THINK THAT'S WHAT DID HIM IN
IN THE END.

38:30.750 --> 38:32.917
WHAT DID?

38:38.959 --> 38:40.458
WHAT AM I MISSING HERE?

38:45.291 --> 38:47.125
HE KILLED HIMSELF, DEXTER.

38:50.709 --> 38:52.041
HOW?

38:52.041 --> 38:56.125
THE AUTOPSY SHOWED AN OVERDOSE
OF HIS HEART MEDICINE.

38:59.542 --> 39:00.834
THAT HAPPENS ALL THE TIME.

39:00.834 --> 39:02.834
PEOPLE ACCIDENTALLY TAKE
THE WRONG DOSE.

39:02.834 --> 39:05.417
HE CALLED ME
THE DAY BEFORE HE DIED.

39:05.417 --> 39:08.667
HE ASKED ME TO KEEP AN EYE
ON YOU AND YOUR SISTER.

39:08.667 --> 39:12.834
I DIDN'T REALIZE WHAT THAT
CALL MEANT UNTIL HE WAS GONE.

39:12.834 --> 39:16.542
SO I MADE SURE THAT AUTOPSY
NEVER SAW THE LIGHT OF DAY.

39:16.542 --> 39:20.875
I WAS LOOKING OUT FOR THE TWO
OF YOU LIKE I SAID I WOULD.

39:23.125 --> 39:25.125
[ SIGHS ]

39:26.834 --> 39:29.000
I'M SORRY, DEXTER.

39:31.834 --> 39:34.333
LISTEN, WHY DON'T WE GO
TO THE CLUB AND HAVE A DRINK?

39:34.333 --> 39:35.583
WE CAN TALK SOME MORE.

39:35.583 --> 39:37.667
NO.

39:37.667 --> 39:39.875
THANK YOU.

39:44.583 --> 39:46.917
THE LEGENDARY HARRY MORGAN --

39:46.917 --> 39:50.875
FORCE FOR JUSTICE,
ARCHITECT OF ALL THAT I AM.

39:50.875 --> 39:52.375
SUICIDE.

39:52.375 --> 39:54.542
IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

39:59.875 --> 40:02.709
SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY.

40:02.709 --> 40:04.333
I HAVE GOOD NEWS.

40:04.333 --> 40:06.500
I COULD USE IT.
WHAT DO YOU GOT?

40:06.500 --> 40:08.500
PROOF THAT JAMES DOAKES

40:08.500 --> 40:11.542
CAN'T POSSIBLY BE
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

40:13.083 --> 40:15.125
YOU'RE LOOKING AT
THE DOCUMENTATION OF A STAKEOUT

40:15.125 --> 40:18.667
THAT JAMES AND I WERE ON
AS PARTNERS SEVEN YEARS AGO.

40:18.667 --> 40:21.166
VERY DETAILED.

40:21.166 --> 40:23.458
WE WERE DOING SURVEILLANCE
WHEN ONE OF YOUR NEW VICTIMS,

40:23.458 --> 40:24.917
LARRY MUELLER,
WENT MISSING.

40:24.917 --> 40:28.417
JAMES AND I WERE HOLED UP IN
A MOTEL ROOM 24/7 FOR TWO WEEKS.

40:28.417 --> 40:30.291
HE DIDN'T HAVE TIME
TO PISS,

40:30.291 --> 40:32.583
MUCH LESS ABDUCT
AND MURDER A MAN.

40:37.542 --> 40:42.542
I RESPECT YOUR COMPASSION
FOR A FRIEND AND COLLEAGUE,

40:42.542 --> 40:44.583
BUT I'M AFRAID
THIS PROVES NOTHING.

40:44.583 --> 40:47.583
NO, IT PROVES
THAT HE WAS WITH ME.

40:47.583 --> 40:51.583
IT'S ALL HERE --
SPECIFIC DATES AND TIMES.

40:51.583 --> 40:54.083
THESE ARE MY PERSONAL
STAKEOUT LOGS.

40:54.083 --> 40:58.041
AND THEY'RE VERY THOROUGH,
BUT I CAN'T USE THEM.

40:59.250 --> 41:01.959
NO. NO.
THIS IS BULLSHIT.

41:01.959 --> 41:03.792
YOU GOT TO BE
FUCKING KIDDING ME.

41:03.792 --> 41:06.291
YOU CAN'T JUST IGNORE
LEGITIMATE EVIDENCE.

41:06.291 --> 41:08.208
I CAN,
AND I WILL IGNORE IT

41:08.208 --> 41:10.750
BECAUSE YOU GAVE ME
NO CHOICE, LADY.

41:10.750 --> 41:13.125
THOSE ARE
YOUR PERSONAL LOGS,

41:13.125 --> 41:14.709
AND YOUR CREDIBILITY
WAS COMPROMISED

41:14.709 --> 41:16.542
THE SECOND YOU FAILED TO REPORT
A PHONE CALL

41:16.542 --> 41:19.375
FROM THE SUBJECT
OF A GODDAMN FBI MANHUNT.

41:19.375 --> 41:21.583
IT WAS A BREACH OF PROTOCOL
AND ETHICS,

41:21.583 --> 41:23.959
AND YOU'RE LUCKY I DON'T
BRING YOU UP ON CHARGES.

41:23.959 --> 41:27.792
WHAT REALLY
PISSES ME OFF...

41:27.792 --> 41:29.291
IS YOU MIGHT BE RIGHT.

41:29.291 --> 41:31.333
BUT IN TRYING TO PROTECT
YOUR FRIEND,

41:31.333 --> 41:34.583
YOU BLEW THE BEST SHOT WE HAD OF
BRINGING HIM IN FROM THE COLD.

41:36.625 --> 41:39.750
COME BACK TO ME IF YOU FIND
EVIDENCE I CAN USE.

41:46.333 --> 41:48.000
I SMELL...

41:48.000 --> 41:49.417
MONSTER MEAT!

41:49.417 --> 41:51.166
AAH!

41:51.166 --> 41:53.458
[ CHILDREN LAUGHING ]

41:54.834 --> 41:57.750
I GOT YA!

41:57.750 --> 42:01.417
[ PANTING ]

42:01.417 --> 42:04.083
All: ♪ NYAH-NYAH,
NYAH-NYAH-NYAH ♪

42:04.083 --> 42:05.709
I TAGGED YOU.

42:05.709 --> 42:07.208
SO?

42:07.208 --> 42:08.834
SO YOU'RE A MONSTER NOW.

42:09.917 --> 42:12.125
REALLY?
YEAH.

42:12.125 --> 42:14.333
COME ON, SOCIO.
I'M SUCKING GAS HERE.

42:14.333 --> 42:17.625
SORRY, ANGEL.
MY LEG'S A LITTLE TIGHT TODAY.

42:18.875 --> 42:21.667
[ CHILDREN LAUGHING ]

42:21.667 --> 42:22.917
AAH!

42:22.917 --> 42:25.166
[ CHILDREN SCREAM, LAUGH ]

42:28.333 --> 42:30.959
IT'S TOO SOON,
ISN'T IT?

42:30.959 --> 42:33.875
FOR THIS.
FOR US.

42:33.875 --> 42:35.750
NO.

42:37.208 --> 42:40.333
RITA, THAT'S NOT IT
AT ALL.

42:40.333 --> 42:42.166
THEN WHAT IS IT?

42:43.542 --> 42:45.583
DEXTER?

42:51.333 --> 42:55.667
I ALWAYS THOUGHT MY FATHER DIED
OF HEART DISEASE.

42:56.709 --> 42:59.250
AND I JUST FOUND OUT
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

42:59.250 --> 43:01.375
HE COMMITTED SUICIDE.

43:03.375 --> 43:06.125
OH, GOD.

43:06.125 --> 43:10.625
I DON'T KNOW WHY
HE WOULD DO THAT TO HIMSELF...

43:12.709 --> 43:15.208
...OR ME.

43:19.250 --> 43:21.709
OH, BABY.

43:28.291 --> 43:29.834
WHATEVER HARRY DID AND WHY,

43:29.834 --> 43:32.417
I CAN'T LET IT DISTRACT ME
FROM MY MISSION --

43:32.417 --> 43:34.250
NOT WHEN FREEDOM IS SO CLOSE.

43:34.250 --> 43:38.083
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]

43:38.083 --> 43:41.208
"FOUND OUT WHERE YOUR CABIN IS.
ON MY WAY.

43:41.208 --> 43:42.709
I WANT MY FUCKING SNOW."

43:44.917 --> 43:46.709
SHIT.

43:53.083 --> 43:56.917
NO ONE APPRECIATES
UNINVITED HOUSEGUESTS.

43:58.625 --> 44:01.917
UNLESS I CAN MAKE THE PROBLEM
PART OF MY SOLUTION.

44:11.625 --> 44:14.083
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

44:17.834 --> 44:19.750
ARE YOU CHAD?

44:19.750 --> 44:22.291
IT DEPENDS ON WHAT
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR.

44:22.291 --> 44:24.834
TIM SAID
TO COME TO YOU.

44:26.125 --> 44:28.208
THE ROHYPNOL.

44:28.208 --> 44:30.208
ROOFIES?

44:30.208 --> 44:31.667
YOU?

44:33.875 --> 44:36.291
YOU'RE JUST NOT
MY NORMAL KIND OF CUSTOMER.

44:36.291 --> 44:39.041
OH, DO STOP TALKING.

44:43.500 --> 44:45.375
GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.

44:58.291 --> 45:00.125
THANKS FOR COMING.

45:04.333 --> 45:06.458
I THOUGHT WE SHOULD TALK.

45:06.458 --> 45:09.208
NO.
I  SHOULD TALK.

45:09.208 --> 45:12.875
I MEAN, I YELL A LOT...

45:12.875 --> 45:14.583
AND BITCH AND COMPLAIN,

45:14.583 --> 45:18.542
AND I KEEP EXPECTING PEOPLE
TO JUST GUESS WHAT I WANT,

45:18.542 --> 45:21.375
BUT I NEVER REALLY SAY IT.

45:21.375 --> 45:24.000
I'D LIKE TO HEAR IT.

45:29.083 --> 45:31.291
YOU ASKED ME
WHAT I THOUGHT WOULD HAPPEN

45:31.291 --> 45:34.000
WHEN THE CASE ENDED.

45:34.000 --> 45:38.375
AND THE TRUTH IS,
I HAD NO FUCKING IDEA.

45:38.375 --> 45:41.333
AND THAT WAS...

45:41.333 --> 45:43.583
EXCITING, YOU KNOW?

45:43.583 --> 45:46.709
THE NOT KNOWING.

45:46.709 --> 45:49.333
WHAT MIGHT HAPPEN.
WHAT COULD BE.

45:49.333 --> 45:53.917
IT WAS ALL POSSIBILITY.

45:55.417 --> 46:01.333
AND WHEN YOU JUST ASSUMED THAT
WE ENDED WHEN THE CASE ENDED,

46:01.333 --> 46:03.041
YOU CRUSHED THAT.

46:07.208 --> 46:09.291
AND I WANT IT BACK.

46:12.750 --> 46:14.375
WANT TO KNOW
WHAT I THOUGHT WOULD HAPPEN

46:14.375 --> 46:15.750
WHEN THE CASE ENDED?

46:15.750 --> 46:16.917
WHAT?

46:16.917 --> 46:20.458
I THOUGHT THE NOVELTY OF
MY AARP DISCOUNT WOULD WEAR OFF,

46:20.458 --> 46:22.417
AND YOU'D GET TIRED OF ME.

46:22.417 --> 46:25.250
OH, MY GOD.

46:27.792 --> 46:30.166
THAT'S THE SWEETEST THING
YOU'VE EVER SAID.

46:30.166 --> 46:31.750
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

46:36.959 --> 46:38.583
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

46:38.583 --> 46:40.750
[ SIGHS ]

46:43.250 --> 46:44.291
LUNDY.

46:48.625 --> 46:51.000
ON OUR WAY.

46:51.000 --> 46:52.291
WHAT DO WE GOT?

46:52.291 --> 46:55.166
A HIT ON ONE OF DOAKES' FALSE
I.D.'s AT A CAR-RENTAL AGENCY.

46:55.166 --> 46:57.083
MAKE, MODEL,
AND LICENSE PLATE.

46:57.083 --> 46:58.458
LET'S GO.

46:58.458 --> 47:01.959
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING ]

47:05.542 --> 47:08.417
[ DOOR OPENS ]

47:11.083 --> 47:13.000
MY HERO.

47:14.709 --> 47:17.792
THIS PLACE
LOOKS LIKE BRAND-NEW.

47:17.792 --> 47:19.959
IT'S MY PLEASURE,

47:19.959 --> 47:22.458
THOUGH I FEEL A LITTLE LOOPY
FROM THE FUMES.

47:25.000 --> 47:28.041
SO HOW WAS YOUR DAY
AT THE BEACH?

47:28.041 --> 47:30.542
[ SIGHS ]
AURI WORE ME OUT.

47:30.542 --> 47:33.208
YOU EVER TRY AND RUN
IN THE SAND?

47:33.208 --> 47:36.834
I NEVER RUN.
YOU'RE A BETTER MAN THAN ME.

47:36.834 --> 47:39.083
I'M GLAD YOU THINK SO.

47:39.083 --> 47:42.875
AND HOW ARE DEXTER AND RITA?

47:42.875 --> 47:46.834
THINGS ARE GOOD FOR THEM.

47:46.834 --> 47:48.208
I MEAN...

47:48.208 --> 47:51.041
I THINK THEY'RE GONNA
WORK THINGS OUT.

47:58.291 --> 47:59.750
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

48:05.041 --> 48:07.041
WE GOING SOMEWHERE?

48:08.875 --> 48:10.166
[ GIGGLES ]

48:11.709 --> 48:15.542
WELL, YOU KNOW,
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO HOLD OFF.

48:18.542 --> 48:19.917
BUT, UH...

48:19.917 --> 48:24.208
I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T WANT TO ANYMORE.

48:24.208 --> 48:26.959
I THINK IT'S TIME.

48:26.959 --> 48:28.709
I NEED YOU.

48:28.709 --> 48:31.709
MM.
YOU CAN HAVE ME.

48:31.709 --> 48:34.959
THE THING IS...
I LIKE IT ROUGH.

48:34.959 --> 48:36.709
YEAH?
MM.

48:38.458 --> 48:40.834
AAH.
[ LAUGHS ]

48:40.834 --> 48:43.125
OKAY.

48:48.125 --> 48:49.500
WHO THE FUCK IS THAT?

48:49.500 --> 48:50.750
SOME GUY I PICKED UP
IN A BAR.

48:52.667 --> 48:55.792
HE'S A KNOWN MURDERER
AND YOUR FINAL VICTIM.

48:55.792 --> 48:58.500
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DO
WHAT I THINK YOU ARE?

48:58.500 --> 49:01.000
THERE'S NO POINT
IN HIDING IT NOW, SERGEANT.

49:01.000 --> 49:03.750
YOU'RE LIFE IS GOING TO REST
IN THE HANDS

49:03.750 --> 49:06.959
OF THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM
YOU PUT ALL YOUR FAITH IN.

49:08.625 --> 49:11.750
I WISH YOU THE BEST OF LUCK.
COME ON, MORGAN.

49:11.750 --> 49:13.959
WE WERE JUST GETTING SOMEWHERE,
YOU AND ME.

49:13.959 --> 49:15.291
YOU AIN'T GOT TO DO THIS.

49:15.291 --> 49:16.959
COME ON.
WE'LL FIND A WAY.

49:18.792 --> 49:21.041
I'M AFRAID THIS IS
THE ONLY WAY FOR ME.

49:22.625 --> 49:26.709
EXCUSE ME.
I NEED TO GET MY SUPPLIES.

49:26.709 --> 49:28.166
MORGAN!

49:28.166 --> 49:30.917
[ SHOUTING IN SPANISH ]

49:32.375 --> 49:34.959
[ BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY ]

49:36.333 --> 49:39.458
[ CHUCKLES ]

49:39.458 --> 49:43.125
YOU ARE A VERY BAD GIRL.

49:45.458 --> 49:47.125
MM.

49:47.125 --> 49:51.250
I'M ONLY JUST
GETTING STARTED, BABY.

49:51.250 --> 49:53.125
BE RIGHT BACK.

49:56.125 --> 49:57.083
WOW.

50:41.583 --> 50:44.458
LILA, YOU WANT A BEER?

50:44.458 --> 50:46.208
[ CAP RATTLES ]

50:48.166 --> 50:50.709
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

50:54.375 --> 50:56.166
JESUS.

51:05.041 --> 51:08.041
THIS IS DETECTIVE ANGEL BATISTA
FROM MIAMI METRO HOMICIDE.

51:08.041 --> 51:10.500
I NEED AN AMBULANCE.

51:14.583 --> 51:18.375
THERE IS NO WAY PEOPLE ARE
GONNA BELIEVE I DID THIS SHIT.

51:18.375 --> 51:22.208
YOU WERE U.S. SPECIAL FORCES.
I'M SURE YOU HAVE  DONE THIS.

51:22.208 --> 51:24.208
WARTIME CIRCUMSTANCES --
HEAT OF THE BATTLE.

51:24.208 --> 51:26.083
BUT NEVER COLD-BLOODED,
MORGAN.

51:26.083 --> 51:29.917
I'M SURE THAT MADE THINGS EASIER
FOR YOU.

51:29.917 --> 51:32.750
MORGAN, GOD DAMN IT,
YOU GOT A CONSCIENCE, MAN.

51:32.750 --> 51:35.542
YOU SAID IT YOURSELF.
YOU GO AFTER KILLERS.

51:35.542 --> 51:37.250
YOU TAKE OUT KILLERS.
I GET THAT.

51:37.250 --> 51:39.792
BUT THIS -- THIS IS SOME
SICK-FUCK RITUAL, MAN.

51:39.792 --> 51:41.333
YOU NEED HELP.
LET ME HELP YOU, MAN.

51:41.333 --> 51:43.250
DON'T WORRY, SERGEANT.
I WON'T MAKE YOU WATCH.

51:43.250 --> 51:44.375
I'M NOT UNCIVILIZED.

51:44.375 --> 51:45.750
NO. MORGAN.
MORGAN, NO!

51:45.750 --> 51:46.959
MORGAN!

51:47.959 --> 51:49.542
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS!

51:49.542 --> 51:51.125
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
KILL THIS MAN!

51:51.125 --> 51:53.917
THIS MAN IS A FELON
WITH A BODY COUNT.

51:53.917 --> 51:55.583
HE BROUGHT IT ON HIMSELF.

51:55.583 --> 51:58.250
MORGAN, TURN HIM OVER
TO THE LAW.

51:58.250 --> 52:00.542
I LIVE BY MY FATHER'S LAW.

52:00.542 --> 52:02.125
[ SAW WHIRRING ]
NO! MORGAN!

52:02.125 --> 52:04.041
MORGAN, DON'T DO THIS!

52:12.291 --> 52:13.875
OH, SHIT.

52:13.875 --> 52:16.583
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

52:34.959 --> 52:36.834
SORRY IT HAD TO GO DOWN
LIKE THIS, SERGEANT.

52:36.834 --> 52:39.333
BUT THERE REALLY WAS
NO OTHER WAY.

52:43.667 --> 52:45.667
SERGEANT?

52:48.583 --> 52:50.333
STAY AWAY.

52:51.750 --> 52:54.500
JUST STAY AWAY FROM ME.

52:54.500 --> 52:57.792
I'VE HEARD
THOSE WORDS BEFORE --

52:57.792 --> 53:00.625
THREE DAYS
BEFORE MY FATHER'S DEATH.

53:04.291 --> 53:07.875
[ Nervously ]
OH. HEY, DAD.

53:07.875 --> 53:11.208
LOOK WHAT I DID.

53:13.625 --> 53:17.834
IT'S JUAN RYNESS,
THE PIMP WHO KILLED THAT GIRL.

53:17.834 --> 53:19.458
I FINALLY GOT HIM FOR YOU.

53:41.667 --> 53:45.041
DAD, WHAT'S WRONG?
ARE YOU OKAY?

53:45.041 --> 53:48.917
JUST STAY AWAY...PLEASE.

53:48.917 --> 53:51.375
STAY AWAY.

53:54.250 --> 53:57.125
IT WAS ME.

53:57.125 --> 53:59.834
THE IDEA OF A CODE
WAS ONE THING --

53:59.834 --> 54:02.792
A GRAND IDEA.
A NOBLE CAUSE.

54:02.792 --> 54:05.792
BUT THE REALITY OF IT?

54:05.792 --> 54:10.000
HARRY WALKED IN
ON WHAT HE CREATED...

54:10.000 --> 54:12.709
AND HE COULDN'T LIVE
WITH HIMSELF.

54:20.750 --> 54:24.083
WHAT, MORGAN?

54:24.083 --> 54:26.125
WHAT NOW?

54:28.542 --> 54:30.875
I KILLED MY FATHER.
